                    <span class="caption d-block mb-2 font-secondary font-weight-bold">Imapact of Plastic</span>
                    <h2 class="site-section-heading text-uppercase font-secondary mb-5">Killing Marine Animals</h2>
                    <p>Millions of animals are killed by plastics every year, from birds to fish to other marine organisms. </p>

                    <p>Nearly 700 species, including endangered ones, are known to have been affected by plastics. Nearly every species of seabird eats plastics.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

